{"tid":2376383,"cid":38,"subCid":0,"title":"維吾爾人被大屠殺","createTime":"2021-01-22T17:53:40.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-02T16:36:15.000Z","uid":286985,"like":80,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"8a20454fdf0bb034a1fd3879a714706e37204d30","tid":2376383,"uid":286985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-22T17:53:40.000Z","msg":"第五篇: 大屠殺 &ndash; 維吾爾人的悲劇<br />\nGenocide 種族滅絕<br />\nMassacre 屠殺<br />\nKilling 殺戮<br />\nSterilize 絕育<br />\nConcentration Camps 集中營<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Eb8h5IYIH8A&amp;ab_channel=HumanRightsManifesto%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DEb8h5IYIH8A%26ab_channel%3DHumanRightsManifesto%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25AC%258A%25E5%2590%258C%25E7%259B%259F&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5BPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=48b45c8b\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=Eb8h5IYIH8A&amp;ab_channel=HumanRightsManifesto%E7%B6%AD%E8%AD%B7%E4%BA%BA%E6%AC%8A%E5%90%8C%E7%9B%9F</a><br />\n<br />\n「我與所有親人失去了聯繫。現在我不知道他們是否安好，是否仍然在世。他們就這樣消失了。」<br />\n一個維吾爾族人的故事。<br />\n一個民族遭受種族滅絕、器官摘取、被囚集中營的故事。他們的基本自由、生存權利，甚至民族的根和文化，都被高壓政權不人道地奪走。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"maroon\">對付共產黨係長期嘅抗爭，<br />\n唔只係香港人嘅事，亦係全世界嘅事，<br />\n希望大家可以幫手分享一下呢個page</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span class=\"gold\">麻煩大家大大力支持<br />\nFollow &amp; Share 呢個page</span></strong><br />\n<span class=\"red\">Facebook:</span> <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/humanrightsmanifesto\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fhumanrightsmanifesto&d=0UfJYUPH4CcS6uVeskuI5BPkB4X9Hpa20B1QJvXseFg%3D&h=6a6d3eb3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/humanrightsmanifesto</a><br />\n<span class=\"red\">Twitter:</span> <a href=\"https://twitter.com/manifestorights?s=11\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fmanifestorights%3